atetimestamp": 1773369253}, {"pid": 860971757, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 10:38", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860971542,45974302,2310]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-03-13 10:37):[/b]<br/><br/>机构上班了， 可能他们确认石油确实死了。。[/quote]<br/>并没有 超跌反弹而已  轮动的技术形态 做做差价可以  上头大可不必", "lou": 1202, "content_length": 61, "reply_to": 860971542, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773369528}, {"pid": 860985681, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 58, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 12:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860981369,45974302,2318]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39615300]名声丶在外[/uid] (2026-03-13 11:39):[/b]<br/><br/>银行，红利，电力这段时间的白线强势板块全部上轨。<br/>证券白酒底部缩量横盘，接下来该轮到谁护盘了[s:ac:闪光][/quote]<br/>应该是科技了", "lou": 1203, "content_length": 17, "reply_to": 860981369, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773374940}, {"pid": 860988130, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 48, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 12:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860986225,45974302,2319]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-03-13 12:13):[/b]<br/><br/>你别骗我啊狼大，给我希望再浇灭更痛[s:ac:呆][/quote]<br/>希望总还是要有的  1.7以下设备ETF还是蛮有性价比的 几个月前1.3涨上去1.9后不是说什么时候买回么 那这个回撤刚刚好 长线配置的时间", "lou": 1204, "content_length": 123, "reply_to": 860986225, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773376184}, {"pid": 860988704, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 12:35", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[b]Reply to [pid=860988472,45974302,2320]Reply[/pid] Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-03-13 12:32)[/b]<br/>之前也给过策略了 只是大家忘记了而已 <br/>比如当时你想原本只打算买十万做底仓  结果玩着玩着就到100万埋在1.8以上的高点了  如果动多几下 可能成本到1.9了 <br/>那哪怕指数再上去 也不过就是等回本而已", "lou": 1205, "content_length": 202, "reply_to": 860988472, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773376505}, {"pid": 860990039, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 12:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860989906,45974302,2321]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41544856]闻空言语[/uid] (2026-03-13 12:46):[/b]<br/><br/>主要是最近外围太差了，不知道这个下轨无脑的买的策略还有没有效。[/quote]<br/>那你长线逻辑变了吗？就因为老美干了伊朗？", "lou": 1206, "content_length": 45, "reply_to": 860989906, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773377260}, {"pid": 860990598, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 105, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 12:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "长线不动有长线不动的做法 我给策略了<br/>趋势上下操作我也给了加减的时机<br/>超短我也偶尔发了方向<br/>你们有没有发现是因为自己没有认清自己是哪类人 适合什么策略乱操作才亏的<br/>之前发的长文也说了 认清自己才能挣钱。", "lou": 1207, "content_length": 188, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773377573}, {"pid": 861004285, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 14:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "4080附近看看第三条腿能不能撑住", "lou": 1208, "content_length": 30, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773384624}, {"pid": 861005450, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 14:58", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=861005283,45974302,2338]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-03-13 14:57):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，银行动作。算是国家队表态了吧？[/quote]<br/>兜底没意思啊 你不懂买什么啊  第三条腿只能看涨起来的确定性 不能抄底的。", "lou": 1209, "content_length": 71, "reply_to": 861005283, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773385130}, {"pid": 861020314, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 40, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 16:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "有个好现象 下午2点后去港股抄底资金蛮多的 这些钱蛮聪明 胜率还可以的", "lou": 1210, "content_length": 63, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1773391808}, {"pid": 861026435, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 13, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 17:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=861024094,45974302,2349]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67086272]冷酷鸡腿堡game[/uid] (2026-03-13 17:19):[/b]<br/><br/>看到新闻了，南向170e<br/>为啥说胜率可以呢[/quote]<br/>前几天他们抄了个底还T出去了  蛮厉害的", "lou": 1211, "content_length": 40, "reply_to": 861024094, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773394853}, {"pid": 861033708, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 30, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 18:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=861031125,45974302,2350]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66907545]ptydd[/uid] (2026-03-13 18:23):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，想请教一下，长线如果因为这次突发事件出现亏损，是适时加仓还是原地卧倒更为合理。之前喜欢腾挪做T降低成本，但是这次觉得特别难，谢谢狼大&amp;#128591;[/quote]<br/>之前也说过了啊 长期周线级别没破 黑天鹅带出来的位置就是加仓最好机会 不然拿什么时候加仓？总不能追涨吧<br/>不过这是长线操作逻辑 不是短线的。短线要看题材的", "lou": 1212, "content_length": 147, "reply_to": 861031125, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773399007}, {"pid": 861037106, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-13 19:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=861034587,45974302,2351]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-03-13 18:59):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大问一下，比如马桶， 想问问140后第二天放量阴你减仓了吗？ 115的0.618位置左右你肯定补了仓位吧？后边尝试摸前高后，再也没突破这个高点是不是也可以考虑把115左右的加仓再次T出？<br/><br/>还是一直锁了没动过？[/quote]<br/>我当时在做别的 AI硬我只做了长鑫博创和FLH的T", "lou": 1213, "content_length": 47, "reply_to": 861034587, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773401129}, {"pid": 861265949, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-0